Dialogs.Dialog: You know what you think of me lately. I feel a little cold...
I thought it was better to listen.
(Well, are you really hurt? It may have been cold recently...)
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore!
In addition, is it useless if we do not stand?
Gaman or something like that... I won't do it anymore.
Gaman... I won't do it anymore.
(Did you forgive me? I don't think I'm convinced...)
Hey, don't you feel cold to me lately?
I don't think it was my fault.
I don't want you to just apologize. I want you to think properly.
Do you think about recent things?
(This is serious...I think it was cold recently...)
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore!
Occasionally... Seriously, it may be necessary.
Sometimes words aren't enough. See ya.
If you think "I did it, I was saved!", I don't know.
(Did you forgive me? I don't think I'm convinced...)
I'm listening, right? I want you to answer properly.
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore!
Speaking of which, did you think you would forgive me?
……Amaenbo may come here? Sometimes you have to be strict and you'll be a bad boy.
I'll be allowed to do it again. Are you in trouble?
There's no such thing! Sorry, Tehe!
(Did you forgive me? I don't think I'm convinced...)
Well, do you want to go home?
sorry. I haven't organized it yet.
Well, do you want to go home?
Well, do you want to go home?
Eh? Have you not forgiven me yet?
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Well, let's go on a date.
No good……. I don't feel like that yet.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Well, let's go on a date.
Date. Is it a position where you can make such a request?
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Well, let's go on a date.
You may try to do something. But still no.
(It's a phone call... Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Isn't he angry anymore?)
After all, let's stop? I can't go with this feeling.
(It's a phone call... Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Isn't he angry anymore?)
By the way, I promised a date next time...
Oh yeah. What's wrong with that?
Of course, it's canceled. Well then.
(It's a phone call... Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Isn't he angry anymore?)
The date I promised before. I am looking forward?
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Can you see me now?
I can't meet you. I don't know what to do when I meet him.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Can you see me now?
Then can you reach here in 10 seconds?
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Can you see me now?
What do you do when you meet?
It's a good thing to work hard at all times...
If you do your best in this way, will you forget all the unpleasant things? ......What?
If you think about me so seriously...
Even if I'm in trouble, I won't help you.
Even if I do my best, I will not forgive you.
Good job. I can't handle girlfriends at all.
Even with such a face, I will not comfort you.
Oh, can you do nothing alone?
……こんなときでもふざけるんだ。
Yeah, I don't want to worry about ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ anymore.
I'm sorry I was dragging forever.
The bad thing is ●. If the ● is solid from the beginning.
No, it's already good. I wouldn't be good without you...
Yeah, ● too. After all, I like ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Yup. I just want to hear it now.
I did my best. I said something terrible.
Yes, the bad one is you. ...... However.
It was a little fun while I was fighting, but...
I'm not satisfied with that. It's a lot more fun to get along with you.
Yup……. It's natural to offend ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Sorry for the bad boyfriend.
A bad boyfriend... I wonder if it's a bad girlfriend to forgive such a boyfriend...
Yup. After all, I don't seem to like it. I'm thinking of another thing.
I'm lonely, I want to get it back.
I came to see you, is it okay?
No, I'm glad. I just wanted to see you.
But if I knew it was coming, I would have prepared it properly.
Don't do that for the sick. Rather, ● helped me.
That's okay. It's enough just to come.
It's bad if you stay so long. I'll be back soon.
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I hope it will improve soon)
●. How are you I came to visit you.
Yeah Oh, sorry? Did you want to be a nurse?
It's decided that you're fine. If you need nursing, of course I'm happy.
I mean... I wish I had made it worse. I failed.
Oh, sorry for staying long. I'll be back.
joke. I have a cold be careful?
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I hope it will improve soon)
Thank you. Wait, I'll open now.
Yeah, it's not that hard. I was getting tired of sleeping.
So was it the right time?
Yeah, perfect. Can you talk to me?
I'm sorry I was talking for a long time. Are you not overdoing it?
I haven't. Rather, I feel better.
I see. But I'll be back soon, my body will be tired.
Yes, thank you. When you go home, gargling and washing your hands?
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I hope it will improve soon)
Hey you. I'm glad to see you
Good, because it's the most important thing.
It's boring... I want to go out.
I can afford something. It seems that my position has been reversed, so I'm a little disappointed.
Though my visit is good. Are you studying properly? Is the byte safe?
You don't have to worry about that. It's your body right now.
I'm doing it properly. You don't have to worry about ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Yeah... that's lonely too. Heal quickly.
I'm sorry I'm worried, I'm fine.
Thank you for your visit. But I was lonely...
Oh. Let's stay with you during your illness.
of course. Thank you? Thank you for your visit.
I showed you that I was weak... This time it is revenge.
thanks for worrying about me. Is it all right now?
This time it's my turn to worry. I want to nurse.
Fufu, lie. No good. You're best when you're fine.
I'm sorry I can't wait to worry.
No. It's been good since I got bored.
Oh, I talked for a long time. Even if healed, it's bad for you.
Even if you don't notice it, your body is definitely tired. I'll be back, so take a good rest.
(I have to get rid of it sooner for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲)
Yup. I thought it was much weaker.
I'm not ready. I was going to look after him.
I talked a lot. I'll be back before I get sick.
If you really appreciate it, take a good rest and heal quickly.
(I have to get rid of it sooner for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲)
Of course, visit. Hey, were you waiting?
Yeah, it looks better than I expected. It's a bit disappointing that the room is decent.
I wanted to take care of everything.
Oh, I'll be back soon. If you make yourself sick, it doesn't mean you're sympathy.
No Listen to your sister and take a good rest?
Yeah, good girl, good girl. See ya.
(I have to get rid of it sooner for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲)
How are you Are you sleepy? I shouldn't do it.
What do you want me to do?
You don't have to do anything
It's pretty good though. I think it's not completely cured yet.
Let's try various things. Such as a folk remedy.
You're surprisingly good at it, right?
I thought I could do more things.
It's probably not what I'm thinking of right now.
Please wait. I'm fine thanks to you.
Was good……. Is it really okay?
Oh, thanks to the visit of ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
I see……. I wonder if I wanted to see a little more when I was weak.
Just a bit. But do you like you who are fine?
Did my visit and effect work?
That's it. Thanks to that, I want to go out ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ soon.
All right. The effect is working properly, right?
